lown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鐘意認屎認屁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"想知更多"},{"pid":"2dccaef57b0966e36d88580c9fb7c1d5163cfa7f","tid":2326544,"uid":14816,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"書又讀唔成<br />\n做狗前分分鐘係啲mk金毛飛街童<br />\n你期望呢啲人有咩好嘅生活習慣/價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d105c777c663adfc22790ce4c98767ac528055","tid":2326544,"uid":1834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T12:05:24.000Z","msg":"權威性<br />\n十個有八個都當屋企仔女係犯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識2/3個警二代都係黃,想自己陷家剷,同家人關係差到閪咁<br />\n<br />\n淫蕩<br />\n男警群組第一單已經係叫雞惹返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心虛<br />\n班自走炮唔認自己係警察,話自己只係公墓員/文職<br />\n<br />\n輸打贏要,貪錢<br />\n當年ICAC成立班垃圾揸槍遊行,其實當年就唔應該特赦<br />\n應該出英軍落幾架坦克,幾隊兵黎鎮壓班狗<br />\n等班陷家剷無得成為香港最大武裝組織高層<br />\n<br />\n貪生怕死(皇家香港警察時期除外)<br />\n唔洗多講<br />\n<br />\n貪權自私<br />\n唔計咩政治案件,班垃圾都會為求扮到自己好似做到野,特登老屈香港市民<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200706/bkn-20200706184438632-0706_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200706%2Fbkn-20200706184438632-0706_00822_001.html&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=4102a72a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200706/bkn-20200706184438632-0706_00822_001.html</a><br />\n上庭畀假口供o既仲有好多單<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%82%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B-%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E8%80%85-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%9B%E5%B1%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%A1-%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE-%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25BA%2582%25E4%25BD%259C%25E4%25BE%2